self._fullPSync.publishName(prefix)
sequenceNo = self._fullPSync.getSequenceNo(prefix)
dump('Publish:', prefix.toUri() + '/' + str(sequenceNo))
if sequenceNo < self._maxPublishedSequenceNo:
    random1 = self._systemRandom.random()
    delay = random1 * self._delayRangeMaxMs
    self._face.callLater(delay, lambda : self.doUpdate(prefix))
